Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:17.55,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:23.88,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:26.54,jojo_ED_EN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}In and around the lake
